Metadata: Northwest Fish Hatchery Newsletter (Volume 5, Number 1 and Number 2, May and December 1989)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program
Two newsletter issues in one entry for 1989.

The following topics are in these issues: Wind-Proof Flow Measurements, B. Bugert; Oxygen Concentrations in Hatchery Work, D. Schaeffer; Number 2: Infectious Hematopletic Necrosis Virus (IHNV) Transmission Studies in Oregon, S. Lapatra; Silt in Heath Incubators, R.J. "Buck" Pierce; Siphon Release of 1986 Brood Coho, W.K. Duplaga and the Washougal Hatchery crew; Bird Predation, L. Schaeffer.
